argin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">This Thursday, two very different versions of t=
he Declaration of
Independence will go head-to-head at Christie=E2=80=99s and Sotheby=E2=80=
=99s in New York. In its 10 a.m. Americana auction, Christie=E2=80=99s is o=
ffering the =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI=
6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dVaTZXOE1FSnZQLUIxWWRuamhrMD0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cH=
M6Ly93d3cuY2hyaXN0aWVzLmNvbS9lbi9sb3QvbG90LXRoZS1qb25lcy1kZWNsYXJhdGlvbi1vZ=
i1pbmRlcGVuZGVuY2UtNjUxOTEwOC8_dXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPVdhbGwrUG93ZXIrLStTVUJTQ1JJ=
QkVSUyslMjgxJTJGMjElMkYyNSUyOVx1MDAyNnV0bV9jb250ZW50PVdhbGwrUG93ZXIrLStTVUJ=
TQ1JJQkVSUyslMjgxJTJGMjElMkYyNSUyOVx1MDAyNnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWxfYWN0aW9uXH=
UwMDI2dXRtX3NvdXJjZT1jdXN0b21lci5pb1x1MDAyNnV0bV90ZXJtPWY2YzYwNjE3ZGE0MmFiZ=
DEyYSIsImludGVybmFsIjoiZjZjNjA2MTdkYTQyYWJkMTJhIiwibGlua19pZCI6MjA1MDM3OX0/=
7fbd628024df6a21bb42060ba3b4b6dc9b684d136b65f4d27b0f8b4591930360" style=3D"=
text-decoration:underline;color:#d40000;">The Jones Declaration of Independ=
ence</a>,=E2=80=9D a handwritten transcription of the original document tha=
t was produced in 1788=E2=80=9412 years after independence was declared. Th=
en at 2 p.m., Sotheby=E2=80=99s New York is selling
=E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1l=
EQUt2UktxclJLZ0dVaTZXOE1FSnZQLUIxWWRuamhrMD0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2=
90aGVieXMuY29tL2VuL2J1eS9hdWN0aW9uLzIwMjUvdGhlLWRlY2xhcmF0aW9uLW9mLWluZGVwZ=
W5kZW5jZS10aGUtanVseS0xNzc2LWVzc2V4LWJyb2Fkc2lkZT9sb2NhbGU9ZW5cdTAwMjZ1dG1f=
Y2FtcGFpZ249V2FsbCtQb3dlcistK1NVQlNDUklCRVJTKyUyODElMkYyMSUyRjI1JTI5XHUwMDI=
2dXRtX2NvbnRlbnQ9V2FsbCtQb3dlcistK1NVQlNDUklCRVJTKyUyODElMkYyMSUyRjI1JTI5XH=
UwMDI2dXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbF9hY3Rpb25cdTAwMjZ1dG1fc291cmNlPWN1c3RvbWVyLmlvX=
